## What This Project Is
SocketSpec is a Python WebSocket framework that provides FastAPI-style
developer experience — decorator-based event routing, Pydantic validation,
and a built-in Swagger-style docs UI at /socket-docs. Developers test socket
events in the browser without needing a frontend.

